{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "sc2-dp-100k-001",
    "name": "StableCoin-DepositPressure-100K-30d",
    "description": "ACTUS: DEPOSIT DEMAND / MINT PRESSURE ($100K Reserve)\n\nGAP ADDRESSED: §11.3 — Existing simulations model OUTFLOWS (redemptions)\nbut none model INFLOWS (new deposits requesting minting).\n\nSCENARIO: What happens when deposit demand surges while reserves are stressed.\n  Day 1-9:   Baseline $500/day in new deposits\n  Day 10:    $10,000 deposit spike (large mint request)\n  Day 15-19: Sustained demand: $5,000/day\n\nCombined with treasury-backed portfolio, answers:\n  'If we honor this $10,000 mint, does backing drop below 100%?'\n  'Should the system auto-block this specific mint?'\n\nThis is the scenario CRE Workflow 2 (reserve-health-check) handles.\n\nContract: PAM representing stablecoin liability\n\nOpen Postman Console (Ctrl+Alt+C) before running.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {"key": "actus_risk_host", "value": "localhost:8082"},
    {"key": "actus_sim_host", "value": "localhost:8083"}
  ],
  "item": [
